node.text: I cannot wait for you to meet Princess Pip and our beautiful little pony familyy starting September 24 on @Netflix💕#MyLittlePonyANewGen @lizakoshy @vanessahudgens @james_marsden @kimikoglenn

user.full_name: The Duke and Duchess of Sussex

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Sofia Carson on August 04, 2021 tagging @sussexroyal. May be an image of text that says 'FOR WOMEN WHO GIVE EVE R YTHING, WE GIVE OUR TIME. ARE YOU IN? #40x40'.

node.text: I am thrilled to support Meghan, The Duchess of Sussex, on her 40th birthday by donating 40 minutes of mentorship to a woman reentering the work force. Will you join us? Tens of millions of women around the world have lost jobs during the pandemic. If you can commit 40 minutes to community service or mentorship today, together we have the power to ignite a global wave of compassion and change. Happy Birthday Meghan & Thank You. It’s an honor to join you in this beautiful campaign🤍 #40x40 #CompassionInAction @sussexroyal
